With the witness, we can close the case and exile them.

274
00:18:45,860 --> 00:18:48,020
I still have doubts about this case.

275
00:18:49,980 --> 00:18:50,580
Say it.

276
00:18:54,980 --> 00:18:56,500
There are prosecutor and witness,

277
00:18:57,100 --> 00:18:58,340
but this case doesn’t make sense.

278
00:18:59,220 --> 00:19:00,820
Fan Yong underestimated the enemy,

279
00:19:01,420 --> 00:19:02,740
Li Shibing is arrogant and irritable,

280
00:19:03,020 --> 00:19:04,100
which made the Jinming Fort

281
00:19:04,100 --> 00:19:05,460
was taken down by the enemy.

282
00:19:06,020 --> 00:19:07,180
The State Yan has weak defense power,

283
00:19:07,580 --> 00:19:09,220
if it was not Liu Pingxing
who rushed to save it overnight

284
00:19:09,380 --> 00:19:10,580
and held the main force of Yuanhao for a few days

285
00:19:10,820 --> 00:19:12,820
with their inferior force

286
00:19:13,340 --> 00:19:14,460
till the relief forces came to support,

287
00:19:14,620 --> 00:19:15,540
we would lose Yan’an too,

288
00:19:15,980 --> 00:19:17,340
and Yuanhao would drive straight
into our territory.

289
00:19:17,660 --> 00:19:18,740
If Huang Dehe and

290
00:19:18,740 --> 00:19:20,100
the servant from Liu Ping’s family told the truth

291
00:19:20,460 --> 00:19:22,260
that Liu Ping preferred life to dishonor
and signed a surrender,

292
00:19:22,580 --> 00:19:24,140
how would he rush to support in time

293
00:19:24,580 --> 00:19:25,660
and fight fiercely for three days

294
00:19:25,660 --> 00:19:26,500
at Sanchuankou

295
00:19:26,620 --> 00:19:27,660
with their inferior force

296
00:19:27,660 --> 00:19:29,500
and hold the main force of Yuanhao

297
00:19:29,780 --> 00:19:30,860
for three whole days?

298
00:19:34,740 --> 00:19:37,260
This case is suspicious.

299
00:19:37,580 --> 00:19:38,420
It should be investigated.

300
00:19:40,100 --> 00:19:41,340
I’ll put you in charge of it.

301
00:19:42,140 --> 00:19:43,460
Before we close the case,

302
00:19:43,900 --> 00:19:45,620
do not torture Liu Ping’s family.

303
00:19:46,420 --> 00:19:47,380
Hold them in detention

304
00:19:48,100 --> 00:19:49,140
but treat them properly.

305
00:19:52,820 --> 00:19:54,660
Yes, Your Majesty.

306
00:20:06,740 --> 00:20:08,860
We were trapped by the enemy and lost the war.

307
00:20:09,340 --> 00:20:12,420
We couldn’t admit the enemy’s power
and our weakness,

308
00:20:12,740 --> 00:20:14,220
that’s why we were fooled by them.

309
00:20:16,540 --> 00:20:19,500
Fan Yong is not the one that should be blamed most.

310
00:20:20,300 --> 00:20:21,060
It’s me.

311
00:20:23,060 --> 00:20:24,140
From today,

312
00:20:24,900 --> 00:20:26,300
I shall eat no meat to redeem my guilt,

313
00:20:26,860 --> 00:20:29,740
and pray for the decreased.

314
00:20:38,180 --> 00:20:41,540
Your Majesty, your majesty,

315
00:20:41,980 --> 00:20:43,460
Congratulations!

316
00:20:45,620 --> 00:20:46,980
For what?

317
00:20:47,060 --> 00:20:48,100
Congratulations!

318
00:20:48,740 --> 00:20:50,860
Just now three physicians

319
00:20:50,860 --> 00:20:52,660
diagnosed

320
00:20:52,660 --> 00:20:53,380
Madam Zhang

321
00:20:53,620 --> 00:20:56,340
They’ve confirmed that she’s pregnant.

322
00:20:57,980 --> 00:21:01,900
Congratulations! Your Majesty,

323
00:21:02,340 --> 00:21:04,460
you might have a prince!

324
00:21:45,060 --> 00:21:45,820
Xiu

325
00:21:47,100 --> 00:21:47,860
Xiu

326
00:21:48,860 --> 00:21:49,660
Prepare the carriage for me

327
00:21:50,300 --> 00:21:51,340
I’ll go to the shop of clothes and accessories

328
00:21:51,340 --> 00:21:52,260
at Maxing street.

329
00:21:52,980 --> 00:21:55,700
= Restaurant of Breeze =

330
00:21:55,700 --> 00:21:57,060
Stop supplying the wine

331
00:21:57,060 --> 00:21:57,940
to tea houses.

332
00:21:58,860 --> 00:22:00,060
Apologize to them.

333
00:22:00,500 --> 00:22:02,420
Tell them due to the rise
in price of raw materials,

334
00:22:02,780 --> 00:22:04,540
Our supplies are not enough.

335
00:22:05,060 --> 00:22:05,620
Yes.

336
00:22:05,900 --> 00:22:08,260
Reduce a tenth of red rice wine

337
00:22:13,060 --> 00:22:14,460
and a fifth of lamb wine in the restaurant.

338
00:22:15,660 --> 00:22:16,260
Oh,

339
00:22:16,660 --> 00:22:17,940
the grape wine

340
00:22:17,940 --> 00:22:19,420
Yuanshen brought back from the west

341
00:22:19,780 --> 00:22:21,420
is going to be a rare thing

342
00:22:21,420 --> 00:22:22,700
in a few years.

343
00:22:23,060 --> 00:22:23,860
Put it back

344
00:22:23,980 --> 00:22:24,940
and stop selling it.

345
00:22:27,300 --> 00:22:29,580
And for the different kind of rice

346
00:22:30,060 --> 00:22:30,940
and spices used for making wines,

347
00:22:31,180 --> 00:22:32,460
buy as much as possible.

348
00:22:32,660 --> 00:22:33,300
Got it.

349
00:22:52,860 --> 00:22:53,660
Aunt,

350
00:22:53,940 --> 00:22:55,900
Are you really going to sell
those dresses and accessories

351
00:22:56,260 --> 00:22:57,100
from the palace?

352
00:22:58,660 --> 00:22:59,900
You have enough money to spend,

353
00:23:00,620 --> 00:23:01,780
plus you have Chief Xia…

354
00:23:05,420 --> 00:23:06,780
If he was reliable,

355
00:23:07,140 --> 00:23:07,980
I wouldn’t…

356
00:23:11,340 --> 00:23:12,380
Silly girl,

357
00:23:13,260 --> 00:23:14,820
who on earth would say
they have enough food, dresses

358
00:23:14,820 --> 00:23:15,740
and money?

359
00:23:17,180 --> 00:23:19,180
You think the world is safe and stable now,

360
00:23:19,900 --> 00:23:21,220
but when you start to be panic,

361
00:23:21,780 --> 00:23:23,740
the world has already been ruined

362
00:23:23,860 --> 00:23:25,140
and it’s already too late.

363
00:23:27,020 --> 00:23:28,020
This is

364
00:23:28,620 --> 00:23:30,460
what I learned

365
00:23:30,460 --> 00:23:31,860
after being in Yongxing Army for more than a year.

366
00:23:32,780 --> 00:23:34,100
= Xia Song, courtesy name Ziqiao =
In conclusion,

367
00:23:34,420 --> 00:23:37,700
defend when the enemy comes,
and do not pursue when they ran.

368
00:23:40,500 --> 00:23:42,940
You’ve been managing Yongxing Army
for a year and five months.

369
00:23:43,780 --> 00:23:45,740
This is your first time to report your work.

370
00:23:46,740 --> 00:23:48,700
And soon you’ll go back

371
00:23:48,820 --> 00:23:50,340
to be the defense officer in Shaanxi

372
00:23:50,660 --> 00:23:52,260
to suffer from the wind and dust in the northwest.

373
00:23:52,780 --> 00:23:53,500
Thank you.

374
00:23:54,700 --> 00:23:57,220
Your Majesty trusted me
with the important duty of defending our border.

375
00:23:58,420 --> 00:24:00,900
I am terrified but glorified more.

376
00:24:02,900 --> 00:24:03,740
I know

377
00:24:04,020 --> 00:24:06,020
you love good tea.

378
00:24:06,340 --> 00:24:07,260
I kept two piece of Dragon
and Phoenix Tea from Beiyuan

379
00:24:07,580 --> 00:24:09,300
in the spring

380
00:24:09,500 --> 00:24:11,540
just for you.

381
00:24:19,700 --> 00:24:20,700
Thank you, Your Majesty.

382
00:24:23,020 --> 00:24:24,420
Zigong said:

383
00:24:24,940 --> 00:24:27,820
"If one is not sycophantic when he’s poor,
and not arrogant when he’s rich,

384
00:24:28,300 --> 00:24:29,180
what do you think of him?”

385
00:24:29,580 --> 00:24:33,820
Confucius said: "That’s okay.
But it’s not as good as the one who’s poor but happy,

386
00:24:34,740 --> 00:24:36,540
who’s rich but courteous.”

387
00:24:36,980 --> 00:24:40,540
Why is it so?

388
00:24:41,140 --> 00:24:43,740
Why it is not as good as the first one?

389
00:24:45,700 --> 00:24:47,740
Your Highness, Officer Ren wants to see you.

390
00:24:49,100 --> 00:24:50,220
Let him in.

391
00:24:50,980 --> 00:24:51,900
You may leave now.

392
00:25:01,300 --> 00:25:01,980
Your Highness,

393
00:25:02,860 --> 00:25:04,980
Madam Zhang had abdominal pain this afternoon,

394
00:25:05,700 --> 00:25:06,900
so I asked Physician Wang

395
00:25:06,900 --> 00:25:07,860
to see her immediately.

396
00:25:08,540 --> 00:25:10,580
But Madam Zhang suddenly raged

397
00:25:11,300 --> 00:25:12,500
and said she wanted to see His Majesty now.

398
00:25:13,540 --> 00:25:14,780
I explained to her

399
00:25:15,140 --> 00:25:16,660
His Majesty was seeing officials

400
00:25:16,660 --> 00:25:18,580
in the Hall of Politics.

401
00:25:18,940 --> 00:25:20,020
But Madam Zhang wouldn’t listen,

402
00:25:20,460 --> 00:25:21,820
and blamed me for neglecting her.

403
00:25:22,820 --> 00:25:24,180
I couldn’t persuade her

404
00:25:25,340 --> 00:25:27,700
and had to ask four eunuchs to stay with her.

405
00:25:28,940 --> 00:25:30,340
So I came here for your instruction.

406
00:25:32,620 --> 00:25:33,380
What did the physician say?

407
00:25:35,260 --> 00:25:36,100
The physician said

408
00:25:36,380 --> 00:25:38,580
probably because Madam Zhang
worries too much and

409
00:25:38,940 --> 00:25:40,020
and

410
00:25:40,540 --> 00:25:42,300
loses control over her emotions,

411
00:25:42,980 --> 00:25:44,020
which hurt her pulse

412
00:25:44,300 --> 00:25:45,820
and the baby.

413
00:25:48,140 --> 00:25:49,220
I’ll go and have a look.

414
00:25:50,900 --> 00:25:52,020
Send someone to wait

415
00:25:52,700 --> 00:25:53,900
outside the Hall of Politics.

416
00:25:54,820 --> 00:25:56,380
Tell the eunuchs with His Majesty today

417
00:25:56,820 --> 00:25:59,020
about the Madam Zhang’s situation.

418
00:25:59,820 --> 00:26:01,460
Tell them to report it

419
00:26:01,460 --> 00:26:02,860
to His Majesty

420
00:26:03,060 --> 00:26:04,060
during the break.

421
00:26:05,180 --> 00:26:05,940
Yes, Your Highness.

422
00:26:13,700 --> 00:26:14,780
I gave you the position

423
00:26:14,780 --> 00:26:16,540
of the Deputy Military Officer of Shaanxi

424
00:26:16,700 --> 00:26:18,340
to support the Military Officer Xia Song

425
00:26:19,180 --> 00:26:20,460
not only because I wanted to do so,

426
00:26:21,060 --> 00:26:23,340
but because many officials strongly suggested.

427
00:26:24,340 --> 00:26:25,700
Not only Xia Song

428
00:26:26,220 --> 00:26:28,340
asked me for your support,

429
00:26:28,820 --> 00:26:31,260
Mr. Xia also proposed three letters

430
00:26:31,740 --> 00:26:33,060
saying the defense of Shaanxi

431
00:26:33,060 --> 00:26:34,220
is not just about military force

432
00:26:34,460 --> 00:26:35,700
but the governance too.

433
00:26:36,620 --> 00:26:39,460
You are the best candidate for it.

434
00:26:42,220 --> 00:26:43,580
I feel honored to have your

435
00:26:43,580 --> 00:26:44,980
and their trust.

436
00:26:45,420 --> 00:26:47,460
I shall do everything
I can to live up to your expectation.

437
00:26:48,620 --> 00:26:50,100
But speaking of governance of border areas,

438
00:26:50,420 --> 00:26:52,020
there are always three things
to attend to, farming,

439
00:26:52,580 --> 00:26:54,300
law and the people.

440
00:26:55,420 --> 00:26:56,380
There’s one person

441
00:26:56,860 --> 00:26:58,940
who’s better than me in all the three.

442
00:26:59,380 --> 00:27:00,700
Better than you in all the three?

443
00:27:03,620 --> 00:27:04,900
I missed

444
00:27:05,540 --> 00:27:06,460
such a talent?

445
00:27:11,020 --> 00:27:15,010
I recommend Fan Zhongyan

446
00:27:15,170 --> 00:27:16,380
to go to Shaanxi with me

447
00:27:16,940 --> 00:27:20,140
and be a Deputy military officer also.

448
00:27:24,220 --> 00:27:27,820
“Transportation of goods relies on merchants

449
00:27:28,900 --> 00:27:32,460
People near and far gather at noon to trade”.

450
00:27:33,060 --> 00:27:36,260
Their business benifits the country
as well as themselves.

451
00:27:37,340 --> 00:27:41,060
Their roles are recorded in the Book of Documents.
How could they be called greedy?

452
00:27:42,700 --> 00:27:44,140
You’ve read

453
00:27:44,220 --> 00:27:46,300
this poem from Xiwen?

454
00:28:06,580 --> 00:28:08,300
You’ve already made the decision before

455
00:28:09,180 --> 00:28:10,180
and even written the decree of

456
00:28:10,180 --> 00:28:12,300
conferring the Deputy military officer of Shaanxi

457
00:28:12,300 --> 00:28:13,820
on Fan Xiwen.

458
00:28:16,420 --> 00:28:17,420
I feel ashamed.

459
00:28:17,860 --> 00:28:20,300
If an official has the talent of

460
00:28:20,460 --> 00:28:21,420
governing a place

461
00:28:21,820 --> 00:28:23,420
reassuring the public
and establishing good practice,

462
00:28:23,900 --> 00:28:25,220
how would Your Majesty not know?

463
00:28:25,980 --> 00:28:27,580
I even dared to make the advise

464
00:28:27,780 --> 00:28:29,940
as if I was risking my life,

465
00:28:30,380 --> 00:28:32,060
I’ve been narrow-minded.

466
00:28:38,020 --> 00:28:39,380
Have a walk with me.

467
00:28:40,180 --> 00:28:42,140
You and Fan Xiwen

468
00:28:42,140 --> 00:28:43,460
will go to Shaanxi to take your position.

469
00:28:43,580 --> 00:28:44,540
It will be a tedious journey.

470
00:28:45,180 --> 00:28:46,020
Let me treat you

471
00:28:46,020 --> 00:28:48,380
with a nice meal today.

472
00:28:54,100 --> 00:28:54,980
Your Highness has arrived.

473
00:29:02,300 --> 00:29:03,780
Your Highness.

474
00:29:25,580 --> 00:29:27,340
Officer Ren said you feel unwell.

475
00:29:27,540 --> 00:29:28,620
Physician has checked on you,

476
00:29:28,620 --> 00:29:29,660
said you are having fetus unsettlement

477
00:29:29,900 --> 00:29:31,620
and gave you some medicine to sooth you
and the baby.

478
00:29:32,180 --> 00:29:33,540
Why don’t you take it?

479
00:29:41,220 --> 00:29:42,620
You have a baby now,

480
00:29:43,540 --> 00:29:44,740
it’s not just your baby,

481
00:29:44,980 --> 00:29:46,220
but also His Majesty’s baby,

482
00:29:46,740 --> 00:29:48,180
and the future prince.

483
00:29:49,260 --> 00:29:50,820
You have the responsibility to take care of him.

484
00:29:51,380 --> 00:29:52,740
Don’t be too willful.

485
00:29:55,620 --> 00:29:57,300
I don’t take the medicine

486
00:29:58,540 --> 00:29:59,660
with unclear effects

487
00:29:59,660 --> 00:30:00,820
just because I want to protect His Majesty’s baby.

488
00:30:02,900 --> 00:30:04,500
Physician Wang has great learning

489
00:30:04,700 --> 00:30:05,660
and high medical skills.

490
00:30:06,500 --> 00:30:07,980
His Majesty trusts him.

491
00:30:09,180 --> 00:30:10,100
How can the medicine prescribed by him

492
00:30:10,260 --> 00:30:11,740
have unclear effects?

493
00:30:13,140 --> 00:30:14,620
I only believe what His Majesty says.

494
00:30:21,180 --> 00:30:23,420
His Majesty is meeting with officials.

495
00:30:24,940 --> 00:30:25,700
We can’t disturb him

496
00:30:25,700 --> 00:30:27,620
unless something happened in the harem

497
00:30:28,500 --> 00:30:30,140
that can affect the state.

498
00:30:33,420 --> 00:30:35,060
I don’t mind if you don’t trust me.

499
00:30:36,580 --> 00:30:37,820
But I can’t break the rules

500
00:30:37,820 --> 00:30:38,700
for you

501
00:30:38,980 --> 00:30:40,300
and go to the Hall of Politics to see His Majesty.

502
00:30:46,180 --> 00:30:47,100
What about this,

503
00:30:48,420 --> 00:30:50,180
if you don’t want to take the medicine,

504
00:30:51,260 --> 00:30:53,100
then just relax and have a rest

505
00:30:53,620 --> 00:30:54,580
and wait till His Majesty’s back.

506
00:30:57,820 --> 00:30:58,860
If I just wait here,

507
00:30:59,660 --> 00:31:00,780
who knows when I can

508
00:31:00,780 --> 00:31:01,820
see His Majesty,

509
00:31:01,900 --> 00:31:03,500
who knows if I can see His Majesty?

510
00:31:03,540 --> 00:31:05,140
Haven’t I been set up by the villain?

511
00:31:17,100 --> 00:31:19,420
What happened? Do you feel pain?

512
00:31:22,460 --> 00:31:23,580
I want to see His Majesty.

513
00:31:30,260 --> 00:31:31,340
you don’t trust me.

514
00:31:31,900 --> 00:31:33,180
I want to see His Majesty.

515
00:31:41,620 --> 00:31:42,300
Alright.

516
00:31:43,260 --> 00:31:44,500
You are having a baby,

517
00:31:44,780 --> 00:31:45,940
and it might be the prince.

518
00:31:47,420 --> 00:31:48,380
His condition

519
00:31:49,100 --> 00:31:50,420
can be seen as something
that can affect the state.

520
00:31:53,020 --> 00:31:53,820
Officer Ren.

521
00:31:54,900 --> 00:31:55,420
Yes.

522
00:31:55,700 --> 00:31:57,220
Prepare a carriage,

523
00:31:57,380 --> 00:31:58,100
soft bed

524
00:31:58,620 --> 00:31:59,700
to send Madam Zhang

525
00:31:59,700 --> 00:32:00,940
to the Hall of Happiness
and Tranquility to wait for His Majesty.

526
00:32:06,260 --> 00:32:07,860
Tell all the officers and Deputy officers

527
00:32:08,180 --> 00:32:09,500
to go the Hall of Happiness and Tranquility.

528
00:32:10,740 --> 00:32:12,180
I’ll tell them

529
00:32:12,420 --> 00:32:13,140
in front of Madam Zhang,

530
00:32:13,140 --> 00:32:14,580
to report it to His Majesty immediately,

531
00:32:15,100 --> 00:32:16,020
no matter who

532
00:32:16,340 --> 00:32:17,620
His Majesty is talking to,

533
00:32:17,620 --> 00:32:18,340
and no matter what

534
00:32:18,340 --> 00:32:19,420
state affair His Majesty is talking about.

535
00:32:21,500 --> 00:32:22,180
Yes.

536
00:32:29,980 --> 00:32:30,660
What?

537
00:32:31,460 --> 00:32:33,100
We are going to continue the war?

538
00:32:35,740 --> 00:32:37,780
After over 20 years of peaceful life,

539
00:32:38,620 --> 00:32:41,100
we can barely see beggars in the city,

540
00:32:42,260 --> 00:32:43,540
and ordinary people

541
00:32:43,940 --> 00:32:45,980
can eat bums and meat every meal.

542
00:32:46,420 --> 00:32:47,380
Every family

543
00:32:47,420 --> 00:32:49,860
can have some cloth and silk at stock.

544
00:32:51,740 --> 00:32:52,820
Now what,

545
00:32:53,700 --> 00:32:55,380
after the market closed for 2 years,

546
00:32:56,020 --> 00:32:57,380
and the war for half a year,

547
00:32:57,940 --> 00:32:59,980
the prices of salt increased fivefold,

548
00:33:00,500 --> 00:33:02,180
the price of grain doubled,

549
00:33:02,420 --> 00:33:03,380
the price of lamb meet…

550
00:33:05,300 --> 00:33:07,340
You won’t suffer from that anyway.

551
00:33:09,780 --> 00:33:12,420
The court stopped the trade with the west,

